open winter
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[high country] a relatively snow-free season that does not allow a clear boundary for safe sheep grazing.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
